OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FDry, fine and warm or very
OL,6,Fwarm, the sunshine perhaps turning
OL,7,Fslightly hazier later. A brisk breeze,
OL,8,Fespecially across hills and along the
OL,9,Fcoast, giving a noticeably cooler feel
OL,10,Fhere.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FWednesday, generally dry and warm or
OL,14,Fvery warm with sunny spells. Lighter
OL,15,Fwinds. Thursday cooler, breezy with
OL,16,Fsunshine and showers. Friday,
OL,17,Fcloudier, patchy rain moving east.
OL,18,FBreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
